body_html:
i found a solution, rebuilt the label_image by adding two lines below

"//tensorflow/contrib/quantization:cc_ops",
"//tensorflow/contrib/quantization/kernels:quantized_ops"

into tensorflow/examples/label_image/BUILD . It works for me (ubuntu 1404LTS, tf0.9-gpu ).

body:
i found a solution, rebuilt the `label_image` by adding two lines below 

```
"//tensorflow/contrib/quantization:cc_ops",
"//tensorflow/contrib/quantization/kernels:quantized_ops"
```

into `tensorflow/examples/label_image/BUILD` . It works for me (ubuntu 1404LTS, tf0.9-gpu ).
